    <h1>The Taj Mahal</h1>
    <p>An Eternal Symbol of Love and Architectural Brilliance</p>
</div>

<div class="content">
    
    
    <div class="image-container">
        <img src="https://tf-cmsv2-smithsonianmag-media.s3.amazonaws.com/filer/b6/30/b630b48b-7344-4661-9264-186b70531bdc/istock-478831658.jpg" alt="Taj Mahal">
